       Ominous Prime and Akron returned to the Ord. The inside of the vessle 
glowed with the vast amounts of Liquid Energon. He wished he could have 
brought Zardus here, but with all the radiation he would have been killed 
almost instantly.
       "Shes getting the Predacon now, sir. We will put her in a strong 
cell." Putnam said, referring to the cells built to withstand the radiation 
of the ship. She would be safe in there.
       "What do you plan on doing with her Commander?" Akron asked, looking 
at Ominous.
       Ominous chuckled. "Well, a ransome perhaps. Or mabey we'll make an 
example out of her. Or mabey we will convert her." He said, and turned his 
attention towrds the map. "But, what ever we do....we need to get that bot." 
He said, pointing at Darkmouses signiture.
       "She has Liquid Energon blood....and with a little modification, she 
could be an Energonian. With Quasar as another bot on our side, I dont think 
we will have much trouble."

--part1_72.6335e7b.2773d8fa_boundary
